      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"1. ZIPPING BJORN did a good job to finish third last time out over 350m at this track (20.44) in a Mix, the second top-three finish on the trot. With a good start should be able to take advantage of the rails draw. Likely to improve sharply this time. 7. ZIPPY TIPPY hit the ground running last start and was never headed to land her maiden success over 450m at this track (25.71). Boxed wide here. Can measure up again. 4. LIZZY BOOST comes off an average run last start when fourth at this track over 450m behind Zippy Tippy (25.93). Safe beginner but has a tricky box to overcome. Has ability and can atone. 2. WITCHY WOMAN can improve on an unplaced run here last time out.\",\"runners\":[1,7,4,2],\"exclusive\":false}",
